### =================================================================
### ORDERS API - PRUEBAS COMPLETAS
### =================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### 1. GET - Listar todas las órdenes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/apiview/orders/

### 2. GET - Ver orden específica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/apiview/orders/1/

### 3. POST - Crear orden para mesa (DINE_IN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/apiview/orders/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "PENDING",
    "total": "50000.00",
    "order_type": "DINE_IN",
    "table": 1
}

### 4. POST - Crear orden para llevar (TAKEOUT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/apiview/orders/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "PENDING",
    "total": "35000.00",
    "order_type": "TAKEOUT"
}

### 5. PUT - Actualizar orden
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/apiview/orders/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "PREPARING",
    "total": "50000.00",
    "order_type": "DINE_IN",
    "table": 1
}

### 6. PATCH - Actualización parcial
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/apiview-rewrite/orders/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "READY"
}

### 7. DELETE - Eliminar orden
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/apiview/orders/1/